2
00:00:00.890 --> 00:00:06.340
<i>Many moons have passed since the Imperial 
Army went to war with the Hellhorde.</i>

3
00:00:08.690 --> 00:00:12.570
<i>The royal princess, Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion,</i>

4
00:00:12.570 --> 00:00:17.670
<i>ends up being taken prisoner 
in the midst of fierce battle.</i>

5
00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:24.800
<i>Subjected to all manners of 
torture day in and day out,</i>

6
00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:29.220
<i>she endures these indignities 
without so much as a peep.</i>

7
00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:28.460
<i>Pop</i>

8
00:00:28.710 --> 00:00:29.210
<i>Pop</i>

9
00:00:29.220 --> 00:00:32.340
<i>She reveals not the secrets 
of the Royal Empire.</i>

10
00:00:31.590 --> 00:00:32.340
Dumb Face-o-Meter

11
00:00:32.730 --> 00:00:35.760
<i>Yes, by no means will she speak.</i>

12
00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:38.320
<i>The princess does not give in.</i>

13
00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:40.990
<i>No, she will never give in!</i>

14
00:00:43.570 --> 00:00:48.160
<i>And so, the torture continues 
today, yet again...</i>

15
00:00:55.130 --> 00:00:57.140
So cute!

16
00:00:57.320 --> 00:01:00.160
Krall Regiment
Snowball

17
00:00:58.030 --> 00:01:00.320
They're healing my soul!

18
00:01:01.580 --> 00:01:03.950
Krall Regiment
Callie

19
00:01:01.690 --> 00:01:03.950
Meow, what's gotten into you?

20
00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.890
Purr-haps you wanna hear a secret?

21
00:01:06.890 --> 00:01:09.160
Actually, the king...

22
00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:09.160
Your Highness!

23
00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:10.990
Why are you offering secrets?!

24
00:01:11.440 --> 00:01:12.740
That was close!

25
00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:14.840
They're just too darn cute!

26
00:01:15.410 --> 00:01:18.210
Isn't it a bit late to 
be taking that attitude?

27
00:01:20.140 --> 00:01:24.130
Princess, it's time for some torture!

28
00:01:38.110 --> 00:01:45.500
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

29
00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:59.280
Princess, it's time for some torture!

30
00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.330
How about it, Princess?

31
00:03:01.330 --> 00:03:05.340
For today's torture, Callie 
loves to snuggle up,

32
00:03:06.090 --> 00:03:09.680
and Snowball loves sleeping 
in people's laps!

33
00:03:10.270 --> 00:03:13.420
It's totally impossible to hold 
out against such cuteness!

34
00:03:13.420 --> 00:03:14.840
Curses!

35
00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:18.010
I bet Her Highness is going 
to spill the beans again...

36
00:03:18.010 --> 00:03:18.830
Hey!

37
00:03:19.310 --> 00:03:24.970
It's true that in the past, I almost gave in 
to Maomao-chan and Hngy-Baby's cuteness...

38
00:03:25.650 --> 00:03:29.030
But I've never once confessed 
because they were cute!

39
00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.050
Now that you mention it!

40
00:03:30.350 --> 00:03:32.820
Wait, you were about to talk just now...

41
00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.100
I held out, didn't I?

42
00:03:34.100 --> 00:03:36.640
A testament to my willpower!

43
00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:37.580
Oh...

44
00:03:37.890 --> 00:03:39.440
Anyway, Krall-chan!

45
00:03:39.990 --> 00:03:41.730
Cuteness alone...

46
00:03:42.310 --> 00:03:44.750
won't be enough to make me fold!

47
00:03:45.190 --> 00:03:47.010
I see.

48
00:03:47.010 --> 00:03:52.190
But you haven't seen the worst 
part of this torture yet!

49
00:03:53.180 --> 00:03:55.280
Bluffing, I see.

50
00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:58.410
Kitties are at their max cuteness 
from the very beginning.

51
00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.620
It can't go any higher!

52
00:04:01.430 --> 00:04:04.890
I knew that all along, baby!

53
00:04:07.730 --> 00:04:09.330
What's the matter, Your Highness?

54
00:04:09.850 --> 00:04:11.110
Well...

55
00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:16.330
Looks like it's started.

56
00:04:17.310 --> 00:04:19.100
Your legs have gone numb!

57
00:04:20.810 --> 00:04:22.080
You fiend!

58
00:04:22.080 --> 00:04:26.070
Could it be that from the moment 
you placed Snowball in my lap...

59
00:04:26.070 --> 00:04:27.320
Yep!

60
00:04:27.320 --> 00:04:29.570
This was my goal all along!

61
00:04:29.850 --> 00:04:33.690
If your legs are numb, can't you 
just move the white cat off you?

62
00:04:34.390 --> 00:04:35.480
Ex.

63
00:04:36.330 --> 00:04:38.000
I can't do that.

64
00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:38.840
What?

65
00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:41.580
If I did that...

66
00:04:42.900 --> 00:04:46.130
I would wake Snowball up!

67
00:04:44.090 --> 00:04:46.890
Zzz
Zzz...

68
00:04:46.870 --> 00:04:48.910
What are you gonna do, Princess?

69
00:04:48.910 --> 00:04:54.800
I can gently take Snowball into my arms 
without waking her up, if you want.

70
00:04:55.750 --> 00:04:57.700
Don't underestimate me.

71
00:04:57.700 --> 00:05:01.220
I am Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

72
00:05:01.220 --> 00:05:05.750
I've fought my way to victory 
while enduring serious wounds.

73
00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:11.540
Compared to that, these 
numb legs are no big deal!

74
00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:16.540
I'll withstand the pain 
until Snowball wakes up!

75
00:05:16.760 --> 00:05:18.130
Really?

76
00:05:18.130 --> 00:05:23.000
Don't forget, Snowball's 
not the only kitty here.

77
00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:29.070
Callie!

78
00:05:29.310 --> 00:05:33.550
Callie loves to snuggle up...

79
00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:35.820
Don't do it, Callie!

80
00:05:38.870 --> 00:05:41.830
I know you want to, but please...

81
00:05:41.830 --> 00:05:43.810
I'm begging you, Callie!

82
00:05:43.810 --> 00:05:47.030
Spare me! Please, spare me!

83
00:05:53.830 --> 00:05:58.040
The princess 
confessed

84
00:05:58.050 --> 00:06:00.450
Are you okay, Your Highness?!

85
00:06:03.050 --> 00:06:05.040
Darn you, Callie!

86
00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:07.650
You may look cute, but 
that's downright mean!

87
00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:09.350
Unforgivable!

88
00:06:09.750 --> 00:06:12.760
I'll never forgive you!

89
00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:17.640
All forgiven!

90
00:06:17.640 --> 00:06:18.900
Your Highness?!

91
00:06:19.310 --> 00:06:22.450
Krall-chan, can I play with Callie?

92
00:06:22.450 --> 00:06:25.000
You betcha, baby!

93
00:06:25.350 --> 00:06:28.280
Here, this is payback!

94
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:30.110
Nuzzle, nuzzle!

95
00:06:30.460 --> 00:06:32.880
Princess, wanna give her a snack?

96
00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:35.320
Yeah, totally!

97
00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:40.780
You're so adorable!

98
00:06:42.090 --> 00:06:44.920
Did you get sick of being held, Snowball?

99
00:06:47.660 --> 00:06:50.630
Ah! A little higher!

100
00:06:51.260 --> 00:06:53.980
They truly are elite members 
of the therapeutic unit.

101
00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:59.920
What did he think of today's secret?

102
00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:05.410
<i>His Majesty actually left early today to 
prepare for important business tomorrow.</i>

103
00:07:05.410 --> 00:07:06.110
What?

104
00:07:06.890 --> 00:07:09.930
Tomorrow is Princess 
Maomao-chan's field day.

105
00:07:09.950 --> 00:07:11.450
Today's Event
Hellholm
Pre-School
Field Day

106
00:07:09.950 --> 00:07:12.990
Hellgrove Park

107
00:07:10.860 --> 00:07:14.790
His Majesty's waking up early to line 
up and secure a spot for his family.

108
00:07:12.570 --> 00:07:15.490
Line
ends
here

109
00:07:15.500 --> 00:07:17.030
I see.

110
00:07:17.030 --> 00:07:19.500
That is of the utmost importance.

111
00:07:21.950 --> 00:07:23.510
Field day...

112
00:07:24.770 --> 00:07:29.040
I'll need to go to cheer her on!

113
00:07:29.350 --> 00:07:32.920
I must make a packed lunch 
and invite the princess!

114
00:07:34.050 --> 00:07:38.060
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

115
00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:44.230
Field Day

116
00:07:42.180 --> 00:07:46.200
<i>Pom-pom, Hellholm, pom pom-pom</i>

117
00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:49.940
Hellholm Pre-School

118
00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:49.940
Hellholm Pre-School

119
00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:49.940
<i>Pom-pom, Hellholm, pom pom-pom</i>

120
00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:53.450
Hell-Lord

121
00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:53.450
Main Desk

122
00:07:50.210 --> 00:07:53.460
<i>Pre Pre-School</i>

123
00:07:53.730 --> 00:07:57.950
<i>Pre Pre-School</i>

124
00:07:57.950 --> 00:08:00.370
Hellholm Pre-School

125
00:07:57.950 --> 00:08:00.370
Hellholm Pre-School

126
00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:06.740
That was the second-year class with 
the Hellholm Pre-School March!

127
00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:09.360
Ah, so adorable!

128
00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:11.720
I don't know them, but they're cute.

129
00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:12.830
I'll talk.

130
00:08:12.830 --> 00:08:14.010
Your Highness?

131
00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:16.590
When's Maomao-chan's event?

132
00:08:16.590 --> 00:08:18.470
Let's see...

133
00:08:18.470 --> 00:08:20.090
It's coming up next, actually.

134
00:08:20.390 --> 00:08:23.250
See, she's waiting at the entrance gate.

135
00:08:23.250 --> 00:08:24.300
You're right!

136
00:08:24.300 --> 00:08:27.190
Hey! Maomao-chan!

137
00:08:29.810 --> 00:08:33.600
The next event will be the 
third-year class race!

138
00:08:34.380 --> 00:08:36.830
Blast it! How maddening!

139
00:08:37.410 --> 00:08:41.700
Maomao-chan's big moment is here, 
yet this camera is broken!

140
00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:45.200
Curse you, humans!

141
00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:48.220
Your Majesty, the humans 
are not to blame here.

142
00:08:48.220 --> 00:08:50.190
You forgot to take the lens cap off.

143
00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:54.630
Okay, everyone who's up next, 
please wait at the starting line!

144
00:08:55.810 --> 00:08:57.330
I won't lose!

145
00:08:57.330 --> 00:08:58.430
Oh!

146
00:08:58.430 --> 00:09:01.540
Insuke's next to Princess Maomao-chan!

147
00:09:01.540 --> 00:09:02.560
Insuke?

148
00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:05.090
M-My little brother.

149
00:09:05.350 --> 00:09:10.860
Inki's Little Brother
Insuke

150
00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.160
Look, over there.

151
00:09:07.160 --> 00:09:07.950
I see him!

152
00:09:07.950 --> 00:09:09.140
He looks like you!

153
00:09:09.140 --> 00:09:10.870
They're about to begin.

154
00:09:11.500 --> 00:09:13.150
On your marks!

155
00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.120
Get set!

156
00:09:16.730 --> 00:09:18.850
They're off to a good start!

157
00:09:18.850 --> 00:09:20.360
You can do it!

158
00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:23.370
<i>Okay, everyone! Best of luck!</i>

159
00:09:23.780 --> 00:09:25.100
Princess Maomao-chan...

160
00:09:25.100 --> 00:09:27.800
Insuke! Go get 'em!

161
00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:30.600
Go Maomao-chan!

162
00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:43.050
<i>Goal!</i>

163
00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:44.720
Awesome!

164
00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.570
Insuke's the winner!

165
00:09:46.570 --> 00:09:48.570
Huh? Is that okay?

166
00:09:48.570 --> 00:09:50.840
Winning against the Hell-Lord's daughter.

167
00:09:51.870 --> 00:09:55.330
She may be His Majesty's kid, 
but this is a fair race!

168
00:09:55.590 --> 00:09:58.210
Insuke! You did great!

169
00:09:58.210 --> 00:10:01.780
Maomao-chan! You tried your best!

170
00:10:01.780 --> 00:10:04.020
That's my daughter for you.

171
00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:06.240
Excellent running.

172
00:10:07.040 --> 00:10:09.560
<i>The field day continues!</i>

173
00:10:27.800 --> 00:10:30.250
So cute, so cute!

174
00:10:30.250 --> 00:10:33.570
It's great seeing these 
young kids try their best.

175
00:10:33.570 --> 00:10:34.900
Princess.

176
00:10:34.900 --> 00:10:39.180
We're going to go help move some 
equipment for the afternoon events.

177
00:10:39.180 --> 00:10:40.780
We'll be back soon.

178
00:10:40.780 --> 00:10:43.320
Sure, see you later!

179
00:10:43.610 --> 00:10:47.160
<i>Next up, the third-year class 
parent participation event,</i>

180
00:10:47.430 --> 00:10:49.010
<i>Tag Team Kangaroo!</i>

181
00:10:49.010 --> 00:10:49.950
Ah!

182
00:10:49.950 --> 00:10:52.090
There's Maomao-chan!

183
00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:54.100
Parent event?

184
00:10:54.100 --> 00:10:55.950
So that must mean...

185
00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:08.430
<i>That's...</i>

186
00:11:10.530 --> 00:11:11.890
<i>the Hell-Lord!</i>

187
00:11:15.580 --> 00:11:16.710
<i>The Hell-Lord.</i>

188
00:11:16.070 --> 00:11:19.640
<i>Guardians, please line up 
at the starting position!</i>

189
00:11:17.150 --> 00:11:18.900
<i>It's my first time seeing him.</i>

190
00:11:20.170 --> 00:11:21.390
<i>Get set!</i>

191
00:11:20.640 --> 00:11:23.290
<i>So that's the empire's...</i>

192
00:11:25.460 --> 00:11:27.410
<i>No, humanity's enemy!</i>

193
00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.070
<i>The embodiment of evil!</i>

194
00:11:31.050 --> 00:11:33.000
<i>Ruler of all monsters!</i>

195
00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:35.720
<i>Their fearsome leader!</i>

196
00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:37.660
<i>A symbol of absolute power!</i>

197
00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.240
Nah, that can't be him.

198
00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:42.030
There's no way that's the Hell-Lord.

199
00:11:42.030 --> 00:11:44.380
Yes, I'm sure he's just a body double.

200
00:11:44.380 --> 00:11:46.680
The Hell-Lord would never 
come to a school field day.

201
00:11:50.800 --> 00:11:53.130
Excellent work out there, Your Majesty.

202
00:11:54.580 --> 00:11:56.360
Geh-heh-heh.

203
00:11:56.360 --> 00:12:03.950
Hellholm Pre-School

204
00:11:56.970 --> 00:11:59.870
I see the princess has come to watch.

205
00:11:59.870 --> 00:12:00.980
Yes.

206
00:12:00.980 --> 00:12:03.380
It seems she's enjoying the proceedings.

207
00:12:03.380 --> 00:12:05.670
Not a care in the world, I see.

208
00:12:05.990 --> 00:12:09.670
Unaware of the hellish fate that 
awaits her in the afternoon.

209
00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:11.340
Hellish fate?

210
00:12:11.570 --> 00:12:16.340
After hearing that the princess was 
here, I made some preparations.

211
00:12:16.700 --> 00:12:18.780
Geh-heh-heh.

212
00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:24.180
For a face-to-face battle 
between the two of us!

213
00:12:31.230 --> 00:12:34.060
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

214
00:12:34.060 --> 00:12:36.900
Hellgrove Park

215
00:12:34.060 --> 00:12:36.900
Today's Event
Hellholm Pre-School
Field Day

216
00:12:35.710 --> 00:12:39.380
<i>We will now be taking a break for lunch.</i>

217
00:12:43.980 --> 00:12:45.940
Wow, lunchboxes!

218
00:12:45.940 --> 00:12:47.980
Whoa, that looks great!

219
00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:49.450
What a feast!

220
00:12:49.450 --> 00:12:51.960
Did you make this yourself, Torture?

221
00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:54.050
I hope you find it agreeable.

222
00:12:54.050 --> 00:12:57.530
Y-You're awesome, Grand Inquisitor!

223
00:12:57.530 --> 00:12:58.980
Yeah, yeah!

224
00:12:58.980 --> 00:13:00.070
Torture!

225
00:13:00.890 --> 00:13:02.130
Thanks!

226
00:13:05.740 --> 00:13:08.150
Yay! Let's dig in already!

227
00:13:09.250 --> 00:13:10.670
Is this another torture method?!

228
00:13:10.670 --> 00:13:12.520
Today is Saturday.

229
00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:15.670
We've never tortured you 
on weekends, have we?

230
00:13:15.670 --> 00:13:17.900
No toxic overwork in the Hellhorde, huh?

231
00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:19.790
I guess that's true!

232
00:13:20.420 --> 00:13:22.070
Time to eat!

233
00:13:22.070 --> 00:13:24.360
Let's eat!

234
00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:26.770
First, some fried chicken!

235
00:13:29.080 --> 00:13:31.990
Mm, so good!

236
00:13:32.240 --> 00:13:35.710
I'm afraid the fried chicken 
is frozen rather than homemade.

237
00:13:35.710 --> 00:13:41.470
Frozen fried chicken usually isn't crispy 
or tender, but it's still good somehow!

238
00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:43.660
What do you like best, Insuke?

239
00:13:43.660 --> 00:13:45.600
The salmon rice ball for me!

240
00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:48.000
I think I like the sausages the best.

241
00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:50.510
They're twice as delicious when 
they're shaped like octopuses!

242
00:13:52.930 --> 00:13:54.710
You're right!

243
00:13:54.710 --> 00:13:55.970
Octopus sausages rule!

244
00:13:59.130 --> 00:14:02.070
It's nice eating lunch outside like this.

245
00:14:02.570 --> 00:14:03.390
Oh!

246
00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:07.360
Maomao-chan's eating lunch with 
her surrogate guardian, too!

247
00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:09.930
That's quite the prime location.

248
00:14:09.930 --> 00:14:12.580
Do you think they used the 
Hell-Lord's authority?

249
00:14:12.910 --> 00:14:15.120
The Hell-Lord worked hard to secure this spot

250
00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:17.200
Last one's all mine!

251
00:14:17.530 --> 00:14:20.080
Ah, there's no more fried chicken!

252
00:14:20.080 --> 00:14:22.280
You don't hold back, You-chan!

253
00:14:22.280 --> 00:14:23.580
Yummy!

254
00:14:23.890 --> 00:14:25.480
The shrimp patty's mine!

255
00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:27.290
Meat, meat!

256
00:14:27.290 --> 00:14:28.850
Fried shrimp for me!

257
00:14:28.850 --> 00:14:29.960
Me too!

258
00:14:30.210 --> 00:14:31.260
Hey!

259
00:14:32.150 --> 00:14:35.850
Make sure you all eat your veggies as well!

260
00:14:35.850 --> 00:14:36.750
Yes!

261
00:14:37.140 --> 00:14:41.150
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

262
00:14:41.970 --> 00:14:45.270
<i>We will now begin the field 
day afternoon program.</i>

263
00:14:44.440 --> 00:14:48.950
Hellgrove Park

264
00:14:45.270 --> 00:14:47.620
Hngy-Baby, they're having their field day!

265
00:14:49.490 --> 00:14:53.910
Our next event is the third-year 
class borrowing race!

266
00:14:54.240 --> 00:14:56.620
All right, time for our final battle!

267
00:14:56.620 --> 00:14:59.070
Insuke-kun, I won't lose this time!

268
00:14:59.070 --> 00:15:01.520
Maomao-chan, you got this!

269
00:15:01.520 --> 00:15:04.480
Go Insuke!

270
00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:06.510
Please let me handle the camera.

271
00:15:07.050 --> 00:15:08.710
Geh-heh-heh.

272
00:15:09.060 --> 00:15:12.660
It seems you've managed to work it out.

273
00:15:13.770 --> 00:15:19.900
This borrowing race is where the princess 
and I will have our face-to-face battle!

274
00:15:19.900 --> 00:15:22.120
I had no idea!

275
00:15:22.100 --> 00:15:26.110
What is a "borrowing race"?
A simple explanation

276
00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:26.100
<i>What is a "borrowing race"?</i>

277
00:15:26.630 --> 00:15:29.860
<i>You run until you reach the piece 
of paper placed on the track,</i>

278
00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:32.070
Hat

279
00:15:29.860 --> 00:15:33.950
<i>borrow the item written on the 
piece of paper from the audience,</i>

280
00:15:33.950 --> 00:15:36.930
<i>and run with it to the finish line!</i>

281
00:15:36.930 --> 00:15:40.170
<i>In other words, a scavenger hunt!</i>

282
00:15:39.910 --> 00:15:42.580
*Children who can't read yet can ask
a teacher standing by

283
00:15:42.990 --> 00:15:47.850
I arranged beforehand the prompt 
that Maomao-chan will get.

284
00:15:47.850 --> 00:15:48.590
What?!

285
00:15:48.590 --> 00:15:51.930
Someone
you
like

286
00:15:49.100 --> 00:15:51.940
Her prompt is "someone you like."

287
00:15:53.150 --> 00:15:56.170
I'm certain that Maomao-chan will choose me!

288
00:15:57.590 --> 00:16:02.940
I hear the princess gets along with 
Maomao-chan, but friendship only goes so far.

289
00:16:03.850 --> 00:16:09.110
I'll show her our unbreakable 
bond and put her in her place!

290
00:16:10.560 --> 00:16:12.820
Geh-heh-heh-heh.

291
00:16:17.040 --> 00:16:19.940
<i>Okay, they're all off to a good start!</i>

292
00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:22.660
<i>They're starting to pick up the 
papers with their prompts.</i>

293
00:16:22.660 --> 00:16:25.160
<i>What will they find written on there?</i>

294
00:16:27.250 --> 00:16:30.630
Someone
you
like

295
00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:30.640
Someone you like?

296
00:16:30.630 --> 00:16:37.010
Someone
you
like

297
00:16:30.630 --> 00:16:37.010
Minivan

298
00:16:30.640 --> 00:16:33.030
Minivan?

299
00:16:33.030 --> 00:16:33.960
<i>Oh!</i>

300
00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:37.020
<i>It looks like Princess Maomao-chan's 
prompt is "someone you like!"</i>

301
00:16:37.020 --> 00:16:38.090
Huh?

302
00:16:38.090 --> 00:16:40.430
What if she ends up picking me?

303
00:16:40.750 --> 00:16:44.120
If the enemy empire's princess showed 
up at the Hellhorde's field day,

304
00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:46.120
you think that'd cause problems?

305
00:16:46.120 --> 00:16:47.320
What?

306
00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:48.350
Isn't it a bit late for that?

307
00:16:48.350 --> 00:16:49.230
Hey!

308
00:16:49.230 --> 00:16:52.230
Does anyone here have a sacred blade?

309
00:16:49.230 --> 00:16:52.240
Sacred blade

310
00:16:53.250 --> 00:16:54.170
You rang?

311
00:16:54.930 --> 00:16:56.900
Geh-heh-heh.

312
00:16:56.900 --> 00:16:59.580
Guess I should get going.

313
00:17:04.170 --> 00:17:06.120
Geh-heh-heh.

314
00:17:07.700 --> 00:17:09.370
Come with me!

315
00:17:09.800 --> 00:17:13.370
Now then, who has Princess 
Maomao-chan picked?

316
00:17:15.850 --> 00:17:18.010
<i>It's Her Majesty!</i>

317
00:17:18.010 --> 00:17:21.000
<i>No one can challenge a mother's throne!</i>

318
00:17:21.910 --> 00:17:24.160
Mama, hurry up!

319
00:17:24.180 --> 00:17:27.690
Queen
Lulune

320
00:17:25.580 --> 00:17:27.410
I won't lose!

321
00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:42.170
I really am quite busy, with my address 
at the closing ceremony and all,

322
00:17:42.170 --> 00:17:46.220
so I would have been at a loss if 
she asked me in the first place.

323
00:17:46.220 --> 00:17:50.750
Maomao-chan was just being thoughtful,
so it's not that she prefers Lulune over me.

324
00:17:50.750 --> 00:17:53.420
Any Hell-Lord would feel the same way...

325
00:17:51.780 --> 00:17:53.420
Slow down!

326
00:17:53.420 --> 00:17:56.680
Maomao-chan's mom is so pretty!

327
00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:59.360
You can do it, Insuke!

328
00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:01.740
Maomao-chan, don't give up!

329
00:18:03.100 --> 00:18:06.850
Your fave

330
00:18:03.560 --> 00:18:06.860
Hey missy, can I borrow that bear?

331
00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:09.170
You betcha, baby!

332
00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:13.600
We're gonna get first place together, Mama!

333
00:18:19.580 --> 00:18:21.530
What kind of punishment <i>is</i> this?!

334
00:18:21.890 --> 00:18:23.080
Hey!

335
00:18:23.080 --> 00:18:25.490
Why can't this thing go any faster?

336
00:18:27.710 --> 00:18:31.980
<i>Everyone's running toward the finish line!</i>

337
00:18:31.980 --> 00:18:34.040
<i>Who will take first?</i>

338
00:18:36.360 --> 00:18:38.470
<i>It's Princess Maomao-chan!</i>

339
00:18:41.300 --> 00:18:43.970
You did it, Maomao-chan!

340
00:18:43.970 --> 00:18:46.600
What a close race!

341
00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:48.690
Mama!

342
00:18:48.690 --> 00:18:50.490
You did great.

343
00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:55.270
Geh-heh-heh-heh...

344
00:18:55.590 --> 00:19:00.520
<i>To wrap things up, let's all dance 
to the Hellholm Pre-School March!</i>

345
00:19:00.780 --> 00:19:04.030
<i>Everyone in the audience, 
please feel free to join in!</i>

346
00:19:04.290 --> 00:19:06.880
Huh? Can I dance as well?

347
00:19:06.880 --> 00:19:08.780
Yeah, go for it!

348
00:19:08.780 --> 00:19:10.980
We do it every year!

349
00:19:10.980 --> 00:19:13.540
We're all ready to go, too!

350
00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:22.800
Hellholm Pre-School

351
00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:22.800
Hellholm Pre-School

352
00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:26.720
Pom-pom, Hellholm, pom pom-pom!

353
00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:30.640
Pom-pom, Hellholm, pom pom-pom!

354
00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:34.390
Pom-pom, Hellholm, pom pom-pom!

355
00:19:34.690 --> 00:19:38.100
Pre Pre-School!

356
00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:43.100
Pre Pre-School!

357
00:19:48.300 --> 00:19:52.340
<i>And now for the closing ceremony 
address from His Majesty.</i>

358
00:19:52.330 --> 00:19:57.630
Hellholm Pre-School

359
00:19:52.340 --> 00:19:54.380
Geh-heh-heh.

360
00:19:54.380 --> 00:19:57.630
I've witnessed all of 
your growth here today.

361
00:19:58.190 --> 00:20:01.210
Today's field day was a success

362
00:20:01.210 --> 00:20:05.360
thanks to the hard work each 
and every one of you put in.

363
00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:09.050
I hope you all take pride in that fact.

364
00:20:09.630 --> 00:20:12.740
The Hell-Lord's body double 
gives a good speech.

365
00:20:12.740 --> 00:20:13.800
Absolutely.

366
00:20:14.140 --> 00:20:16.700
All of you here...

367
00:20:18.110 --> 00:20:21.080
get these bear medals as a reward!

368
00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:31.920
Missy!

369
00:20:33.010 --> 00:20:34.510
Maomao-chan!

370
00:20:34.510 --> 00:20:35.590
Yay!

371
00:20:36.060 --> 00:20:38.630
I saw how great you did out there!

372
00:20:38.630 --> 00:20:39.780
Yeah!

373
00:20:39.780 --> 00:20:42.880
I got to be number one!

374
00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.290
Mm-hmm!

375
00:20:44.780 --> 00:20:46.370
Hello there.

376
00:20:47.130 --> 00:20:49.800
Thank you for always looking 
after my daughter.

377
00:20:49.800 --> 00:20:50.900
Not at all!

378
00:20:50.900 --> 00:20:54.180
It's always a pleasure 
to be tortured by her.

379
00:20:55.980 --> 00:20:57.950
<i>Maomao-chan's mother...</i>

380
00:20:58.350 --> 00:21:00.540
<i>She seems so nice.</i>

381
00:21:04.050 --> 00:21:07.060
Bye-bye, missy!

382
00:21:07.060 --> 00:21:08.680
See you later!

383
00:21:08.680 --> 00:21:10.320
Bye-bye!

384
00:21:10.590 --> 00:21:13.630
'Tis time for us to make 
our return, Princess.

385
00:21:13.630 --> 00:21:16.580
Princess-chan, if you don't hurry up...

386
00:21:16.580 --> 00:21:18.210
We'll leave you behind!

387
00:21:18.210 --> 00:21:20.750
Sorry! I'll be right there!

388
00:21:28.740 --> 00:21:31.010
That was so much fun!

389
00:21:31.060 --> 00:21:35.060
The princess 
confessed

390
00:21:33.370 --> 00:21:34.480
Why?

391
00:23:06.610 --> 00:23:08.280
Maomao-chan!

392
00:23:08.850 --> 00:23:10.590
Which picture book should I...

393
